snippet.title: LongPlay a Indie | Derelict (2011) a mix of System Shock , Aliens and Space Hulk
snippet.description:
What would you get if you would mix System Shock , Aliens and Space Hulk .... this game by Erik Hogan

A hidden gem in the wast empty space of the net ... get it from here http://earok.net/
